CustomField.description: The margin to be earned by the investor OR margin purchased at. SGPRT-3852
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The margin to be earned by the investor OR margin purchased at. If Variable: input total margin in % above the applicable base rate quoted to client. If below, input with minus symbol. If Fixed: input all-in fixed rate in %. If Preference Share: input the applicable % of Prime as quoted to client. If Insurance: Weighted Average insurance premium in %
CustomField.label: Distribution Margin (%)
